rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mb-hfpflo-670\">Tracker for OVO credential</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mb-aj8zw8-671\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/u/1/d/1IYVhcOZQlrZv-9YhSxpD8XqKiU5Cd0ydfjJ2-TfrNPs/edit\"><u>OVO MID Tracker</u></a></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mc-dn1s54-672\">[OVO] Template letter</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mc-ctsgcq-673\">statement letter format for merchant if they want to migrate their OVO to us</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mc-uhhi78-674\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/u/1/d/1vYnkzesGmyBl0SCkKMnEhFf0vzdPkIfrZsaz0bD1pDM/edit\"><u>[OVO] Template letter</u></a></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mc-h6c9ue-675\">OVO Login to Submit &amp; Check Partner’s Feedback</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mc-3o50g6-676\">A platform between MO &amp; OVO for merchant’s submission</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mc-spfkyl-677\"><br type=\"inline\">User : fauzal@xendit.co</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5md-s4o1tp-679\">Pass : Merchantops16!<br type=\"inline\">*Will announce to slack channel; merchantops-id-announcement if we change the password</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5md-a12x19-681\"><a href=\"https://simpanberkas.ovo.id/WebInterface/login.html\"><u>OVO Login to Submit &amp; Check Partner’s Feedback</u></a></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5md-qng5w2-682\">OVO Submission Template</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszoui8-fi4maj-329\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5md-760cb8-683\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/14eJY9cy0VyJ8XjkwEOxOEAEvM2fH_Rn2oKB4UgTTIVo/edit#gid=947900899\"><u>TEMPLATE XENDIT TO OVO 2022</u></a></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmkat5me-t2xt9s-684\"><a id=\"_vyzhr5n53e3z\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmkat5me-fpoqql-685\"><a id=\"_owb1e8ihnjl8\" display=\"false\"></a>Eligibility</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5me-89w5af-686\"><strong>Entity Type</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5me-t3gpcx-687\"><strong>Can Apply for OVO?</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5me-c1rfow-688\">Indonesian Entity (PT/CV/Yayasan)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5me-i6z8mi-689\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5me-ycbj7i-690\">Indonesian Entity (Perseroan perorangan/PP)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mf-mosox2-691\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mf-835loj-692\">Indonesian Individual</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mf-6wns6z-693\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mf-fartyr-694\">Foreign Entity</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mf-rdyrb1-695\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mg-jhxkvf-696\">Foreign Individual</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mg-r964s8-697\">❌</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mmkat5mg-42zkdg-698\"><a id=\"_ua1gk41r86em\" display=\"false\"></a>Industry Restriction</h2><ul data-block-id=\"mmkat5mg-2mn1s5-699\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mg-refec4-700\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouia-y37bp3-330\">None, as long as merchant pass Xendit’s KYC process</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"mmkat5mg-3wv5j1-701\"><a id=\"_6c0oxkffxx60\" display=\"false\"></a>Merchant Requirements </h2><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mg-kancyc-702\">Below are the requirements that a merchant has to submit, whether it’s upon onboarding or application request </p><h3 data-block-id=\"mmkau6eu-jisih1-966\">Legal Documents</h3><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mg-l6wc0d-704\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mg-rcloth-705\"><strong>Requirements</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mh-nes585-706\">Individual</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ol data-block-id=\"mmkat5mh-kbqicx-707\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mh-zo0aha-708\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouia-o8ium0-331\">KTP/Passport/Kitas</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mh-s1uzvg-709\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouia-fdfkau-332\">Website/apps/Socmed</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mh-ub6a37-710\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouib-9o6wgi-333\">Logo size 200 x200 Pixel </p></li></ol></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mh-aqvvvg-711\">Local Entity</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ol data-block-id=\"mmkat5mh-ziqeus-712\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mh-gvxhhl-713\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouib-av4lbw-334\">NPWP company</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mh-an7k2o-714\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouib-ujmkak-335\">ID Card (KTP) /Passport/ Kitas</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mh-8v5bfn-715\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouib-9alg0q-336\">PIC Name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mh-vqbr08-716\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouib-nv0si8-337\">PIC Phone Number</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mh-gh8j8o-717\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouib-h075ha-338\">Website/apps/Socmed</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mi-u50ece-718\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouib-1v9voc-339\">Logo size 200x200</p></li></ol></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mi-3ilwes-719\">Foreign Entity</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ol data-block-id=\"mmkat5mi-30e94p-720\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mi-m75sa4-721\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouib-xiokcx-340\">ID Card (KTP) /Passport/Kitas</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mi-l6h0cb-722\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouib-he4vk6-341\">Tax Business ID</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mi-mmrgaj-723\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouib-ftks6x-342\">PIC Name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mi-s11eta-724\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouib-h1joxp-343\">PIC phone number</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mi-fdvbv5-725\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouic-yggt7c-344\">Website/apps/Socmed</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mi-5r2se7-726\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouic-q5ns73-345\">Logo size 200x200</p></li></ol></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h3 data-block-id=\"mmkauhuh-cuvks5-967\">Website Requirements</h3><h1 data-block-id=\"mmkat5mi-zswwhm-727\"><a id=\"_utjlh7t85x90\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mi-3l3ful-728\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mi-z2sque-729\"><strong>Requirements</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mj-3outch-730\">Website Requirements</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ol data-block-id=\"mmkat5mj-o4lmlf-731\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mj-uechal-732\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouic-thw2zy-346\">No Personal Social Media, No Facebook, No E-commerce and Micro-Ecommerce</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mj-ot7r4v-733\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouic-60qa2a-347\">If a website, website must be active and fully running, meaning:</p><ol data-block-id=\"mmkat5mj-yn0qmr-734\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mj-6nzb65-735\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouic-k0c9sf-348\">Link is accessible</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mj-ab3g1x-736\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouic-vmz9yq-349\">Show product/ service</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mj-bdog8d-737\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouic-5a1861-350\">Price in IDR</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mj-uxezgy-738\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouid-a19qpy-351\">Not a template or “coming soon” website</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mj-vgx7xu-739\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouid-vudk51-352\">If an app, app is listed in PlayStore / AppStore</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mj-it12by-740\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouid-2o7cfs-353\">For social media need payment flow</p></li></ol></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmkat5mj-hjkf59-741\"><a id=\"_p97grktq5ar4\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmkat5mj-rzsik0-742\"><a id=\"_uud9e0o6t4io\" display=\"false\"></a>Activation SLA</h2><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mj-ec2ju0-743\">OVO activated in 3 working days from the date merchant submits complete requirements to MO</p><h2 data-block-id=\"mmkat5mj-dpwglv-744\"><a id=\"_qn0mmtfunx4k\" display=\"false\"></a>Onboarding Steps</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mj-tn3f6z-745\">Category</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mk-mm42ck-746\">Steps</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mk-dm5bss-747\">Action</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mk-fqhybv-748\">Process Owner</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mk-18kore-749\">Merchant applies for OVO</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mk-rvdg78-750\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mk-f5djq7-751\">Merchant submit application from their Dashboard </p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5ml-jmr0go-752\">Merchant</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"19\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5ml-dlsq79-753\">MO Process Merchant’s Application</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5ml-8x8vhq-754\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5ml-uhg76f-755\">Open Admin Dashboard → “Channel activation”  →select OVO tab on the top left hand corner</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5ml-5b7y7r-756\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5ml-u3m2w7-757\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-wk37s1l5.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mm-wf9q37-758\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mm-ni42n9-759\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mm-d1jmm2-760\">Click EDIT to see merchant’s details and required docs. </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mm-iu1d9v-761\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5mm-xb7x6i-762\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-jqa7hr9d.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mm-fm3xgw-763\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mm-omcdqd-764\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mm-xjrkkb-765\">Once done click Edit to edit information</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mm-rl25b1-766\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5mm-oreirg-767\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-tryf3dfo.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mn-xa0gyw-768\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mn-h00rnk-769\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mn-0kaxf5-770\">Please fill for this section </p><ul data-block-id=\"mmkat5mn-1ccv06-771\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mn-1bpocp-772\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouig-qmlemq-354\">Merchant Category, for this we need to click their website (we can find their web in channel activation dashboard, see below pic) in their AD information to know the category from OVO,<br type=\"inline\">*)<em>Please don’t choose Online Shopping, Shopping, Digital Content, Shoes, and Digital Product due to we need give detail category </em></p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mn-ey3m4q-774\"><em><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5mn-rgxckp-775\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-bku15h1y.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mn-2khb6a-776\"><strong><em><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5mn-zt7oxf-777\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-9rev3yma.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></em></strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mmkat5mn-2nyd9w-778\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mn-rgtbsg-779\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouig-mexh7s-355\"> if Website is inaccessible, we need to request for alternative websites using this <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1NBuwm4jWCmUt3COEdLoOyaHLOGHS-I3rmuI690wKoLw/edit#gid=1546336929\"><u>sheet</u></a>. </p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-8pau84-780\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-1gjlht-781\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-b5fp47m3.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-utq0wh-782\">*<em>) Email will be sent automatically through Zapier</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-97e23a-783\">How to fill the sheet : </p><ul data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-hnup0x-784\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-1rybbk-785\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouig-jawa62-356\">Merchant name : fill with merchant business/legal name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-mizyf9-786\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouih-y8gwpt-357\">Merchant business email : fill with merchant’s email</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-fqz3xw-787\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouih-wa8f7c-358\">CC alternative email merchant : fill with merchant’s other email <em>(we can find it on Customer Management AD ‘Authorized Signatory Email’)</em></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-ijjjtq-788\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouih-5prmtx-359\">CC sales : fill with Xendit sales PIC (can be found at Admin Dashboard CA)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-4zkoeg-789\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouih-3yje0q-360\">CC 1 : fill with email <em>can be MO Agent’s/ Merchant’s (we can find it on Customer Management AD ‘PIC Email’)</em> </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-pd7o19-790\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouih-ejop1w-361\">Details : fill by choosing the dropdown list based on missing requirements </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-is1ue6-791\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouih-02odnr-362\">Message : leave it blank (will be auto generated when we have chosen the  details) </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-r4kzhi-792\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouih-ix1cpf-363\">Send an email? : fill with ✔ if the data filled are correct </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-iai2zz-793\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouih-yd7zlc-364\">Put your name on the on column after ✔ </p></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-eirclt-794\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-emr2o5-795\">6</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-pue3to-796\">Update this section based on their information from customer management</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-syfini-797\"><em>*updated 22/12/2021 for individual merchants we can leave NPWP No. blank</em></p><ul data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-v75xxi-798\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mo-en1ih1-799\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouih-mduydu-365\">Please make sure to put right MDR <br type=\"inline\">Non digital local: 1.5%<br type=\"inline\">Digital local: 2.73%<br type=\"inline\">Non digital foreign: 2.09%<br type=\"inline\">Digitalforeign: 3.18%</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mp-az9oso-804\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouih-1i6mkq-366\">If the MDR is mismatch with business category can uncheck ‘automatically calculate MDR’ and manually type the correct one&nbsp;<img data-block-id=\"mmkat5mq-yr9j41-805\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-7ghpr13v.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mq-e9flyc-806\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mq-lqslsp-807\">7</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mq-16fnm9-808\">We don’t need to complete address fields and clicking fetch geocode, because this part will automated fill when we download the .xls file, just to make sure merchant address only contain:  </p><ul data-block-id=\"mmkat5mq-zbbzgk-809\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mq-dij1hg-810\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouii-mqt7pz-367\">Street name (no need RT /RW)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mq-eb3zr1-811\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouii-7tietg-368\">Sub District (kelurahan)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mr-00y8du-812\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouii-i427pt-369\">District (kecamatan)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mr-17bxng-813\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouii-edv4r6-370\">Regency (kabupaten)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mr-pu0gyn-814\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouii-g3z6vy-371\">Province</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5mr-47ipzs-815\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouii-7ygqaj-372\">Postal code</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mr-vk19h8-816\">For foreign entities, please use Xendit address:<br type=\"inline\">Menara Sentraya, Jl. Iskandarsyah Raya No.1A, RT.3/RW.1, Melawai, Kebayoran Baru, South Jakarta City, Jakarta 12160</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mr-twythd-818\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mr-agthjh-819\">8</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mr-h0hga6-820\">Latitude and Longitude will be automatically fetched when we generate the sheet, so we these can be left black</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mr-pozwdj-821\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mr-z1emz9-822\">9</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5ms-o2szc9-823\">Once completed, click save</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5ms-i5wgdz-824\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5ms-fxe3mg-825\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-u67t62xe.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5ms-jnp0sa-826\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5ms-727rlm-827\">10</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5ms-ifhr0o-828\">For the status just let it be in <em>new_submission</em> because it will be automatically updated when we generate the sheet  </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5ms-iv8u8r-829\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5ms-cpuq02-830\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-e7s3dkkj.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5ms-yrjhw2-831\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5ms-my30ps-832\">11</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mt-kkpkwd-833\">After completely filling in all merchants, click 3 dots choose Download XLSX button<img data-block-id=\"mmkat5mt-0mfi7c-834\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-n93nrx2p.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mt-80upol-835\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mt-6b2qpv-836\">12</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mt-unbe0w-837\">Pick the date you want to generate and click download </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mt-vufoer-838\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5mt-pt2o65-839\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-vj5ik1st.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mt-uy1dtb-840\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mt-u6bsqe-841\">13</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mu-t3z50r-842\">Below is the sample sheet that we have downloaded</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mu-lc0aht-843\"><em><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5mu-bmgvsz-844\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-opfr1p2s.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></em></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mu-o2jh31-845\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mu-wbs0mz-846\">14</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mu-2qisvp-847\">Open <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/14eJY9cy0VyJ8XjkwEOxOEAEvM2fH_Rn2oKB4UgTTIVo/edit?gid=947900899#gid=947900899\"><u>Xendit to OVO DD.MM.YY</u></a> to match the placement of data from the download sheet on the dashboard to the OVO template</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mu-603m2r-848\">Copy only this column data:<br type=\"inline\">Merchant Name\t</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mu-2imx98-850\">Store Code\t</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mu-pwnlo5-851\">Store Name</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mu-oxk4ca-852\">Category</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mu-amweb6-853\">Merchant Logo (optional)\t</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mu-ovd578-854\">MDR\t</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mu-n9ibgk-855\">Merchant PIC Name\t</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mu-9xzhkb-856\">Merchant PIC Phone No.\t</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mu-zpfj2m-857\">Website</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mu-qw3moz-858\">App\t</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mu-fb4457-859\">Entity Type</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mv-xq5sbo-860\">MDR</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mv-nl04dt-861\">KTP No. / KITAS No.\t</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mv-tm54je-862\">Link Dokumen KTP / KITAS\t</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mv-w1j2w4-863\">NPWP No.\t</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mv-h6zzyz-864\">Link Dokumen NPWP\t</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mv-u1snua-865\">Link Dokumen PG Switch</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mv-oqpvvv-866\">*can put payment flow file link on the last column </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mv-dzerrl-867\">Gdrive to store payment flow <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1UvBVVlM_HnA61Q-2VXI0xhNBLoN9vodq?usp=drive_link\"><u>OVO KITAS/KTP/Payment Flow</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouim-6ypj6m-373\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mv-ebnoma-868\">15</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mv-q9ys0h-869\">Upload the file you have downloaded on above step to FTP using this link <a href=\"https://simpanberkas.ovo.id/WebInterface/login.html\"><u>https://simpanberkas.ovo.id/WebInterface/login.htm</u></a> </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mv-cqpbpd-870\"><br type=\"inline\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5mv-q3jxa9-873\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-2kb2fnhm.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mw-zp8ec4-874\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mw-uhahmr-875\">16</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mw-586os7-876\">On simpanberkas page, choose merchant_onboarding folder</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mw-wnur3n-877\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5mw-eu9rfh-878\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-f2dj2y6j.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mw-6vnkub-879\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mw-5uxo88-880\">17</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mw-g5czp6-881\">Choose request_merchant_by_Xendit</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mw-i7zynu-882\"><strong><em>*name the file Xendit[space]submission date(dd.mm.yy)[space]vol 1 </em></strong><br type=\"inline\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5mx-sb7rqa-885\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-evkmb7wm.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mx-fp66dr-886\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mx-3ien21-887\">18</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mx-nxh11g-888\">Upload files <br type=\"inline\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5mx-ghxnaz-891\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-c25lm2k5.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mx-q4k0o2-892\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mx-6f1wx5-893\">19</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5my-x7ggpq-894\">Once we have finished uploading  in the OVO Dashboard, inform the submission to OVO team via private slack channel  “#partnerchannel-xendit-ovo”. Via workflow, See example below <br type=\"inline\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5my-p1q4yq-897\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-ne82cae0.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5my-2mszhl-898\">Click submit</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5my-i0uyhc-899\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5my-4qxnx4-900\">20</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5my-zpa5m1-901\">Please copy paste our .xls current submission to <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1IYVhcOZQlrZv-9YhSxpD8XqKiU5Cd0ydfjJ2-TfrNPs/edit#gid=1949897328\"><u>OVO mid tracker</u></a> </p><ul data-block-id=\"mmkat5my-4oa0xh-902\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5my-1l18qk-903\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouip-g3so0f-374\">Fill date of sub</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5my-uecfuy-904\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouip-cvrpvr-375\">Copy in .xls from merchant name and paste to column C (merchant name)</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5my-88ty4s-905\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5my-movxna-906\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-3y938tii.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouip-eg384h-376\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mz-y2x2pm-907\">Approval from partner</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mz-2nsm6e-908\">21</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mz-owv93a-909\">Once OVO team has finished reviewing our submission, they will inform us from slack channel on the thread of our workflow  like below example</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mz-xnswdu-910\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5mz-6e6zv9-911\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-islyh8r0.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mz-vedhtr-912\">OVO team</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"5\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mz-xufoz0-913\">Merchant activation process</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mz-nw09lr-914\">22</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5mz-feb1wp-915\">We can then check on OVO dashboard (<a href=\"https://simpanberkas.ovo.id/WebInterface/login.html\"><u>https://simpanberkas.ovo.id/WebInterface/login.htm</u></a> ) by choosing status_merchant_by_OVO <br type=\"inline\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5n0-66w8bi-918\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-yfc7pjnb.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n0-xnq6lo-919\">Tips: filter on modified column to see the newest file </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n0-7r0zyz-920\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5n0-mpm76b-921\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-7p4tfd2j.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n0-xgrkql-922\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n0-tuvahx-923\">23</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n0-ivr9cf-924\">For the activation we just need to upload the downloaded sheet from simpan berkas by clicking upload feedback </p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n0-s0dwsr-925\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5n0-3e4f2x-926\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-2db5rvi1.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n0-6lw4lz-927\">Will appear Upload .xls box → select file → select the file that was previously downloaded from ‘simpanberkas’ OVO → Open</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n0-iptjmu-928\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5n0-vflgs3-929\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-yw1gmpqh.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n0-5w9kpn-930\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n0-4kcy0d-931\">24</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n0-p0818n-932\">After choosing file, will appear box menu for merchant list who already have complete credentials for CA OVO activation according to the uploaded excel file → click continue →  tick all checkbox → click continue</p><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n1-dzh1kq-933\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5n1-cuap15-934\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-9p69ulz5.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouis-vnxifd-377\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n1-13kww6-935\">25</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n1-fuom7v-936\">Update the activated OVO credential on the <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1IYVhcOZQlrZv-9YhSxpD8XqKiU5Cd0ydfjJ2-TfrNPs/edit#gid=1949897328\"><u>OVO mid tracker</u></a> according to the submission date.</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmkat5n1-7vb8l4-937\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5n1-uw172o-938\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouis-agowrb-378\">Fill TID (row Z)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5n1-p8s1tq-939\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouis-8502mn-379\">MID (row AA)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5n1-ilrbhv-940\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouis-tp3k3q-380\">Merchant ID (row AB)</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n1-apil7m-941\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5n1-6fibim-942\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-2u6kie97.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouis-2bpuwd-381\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n1-5srezw-943\">26</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n1-bizwac-944\">when there is a merchant that is not approved by OVO listed in the feedback file from OVO, what we do is:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmkat5n1-sh093w-945\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5n1-96yx1l-946\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouit-iuxey7-382\">Check the reason OVO does not approve the merchant</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n1-cjmhrz-947\"><img data-block-id=\"mmkat5n2-jaijvp-948\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-ovo-image-zs36p7om.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><ul data-block-id=\"mmkat5n2-ax5hns-949\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5n2-jsfsqh-950\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouit-xe3h8d-383\">The following reasons are often given by OVO</p></li></ul><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n2-rfal8v-951\"><strong>OVO’s Reason</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n2-g5vp74-952\"><strong>What do we do?</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n2-m2z2mh-953\">wrong MDR (e.g.: mohon rubah MDR menjadi 2.7%)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mmkat5n2-6ezmfv-954\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5n2-nvxxh9-955\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouit-oe5mkh-384\">Open Admin Dashboard → channel activation tab → click OVO → search merchant by its merchant name → click edit</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5n2-39zau9-956\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouit-ya70hh-385\">Revise MDR based on OVO remarks → click save </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5n2-ssejm9-957\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouit-656mhl-386\"><strong>Please change the billing rates on CM too.</strong></p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkat5n2-ca6326-958\">Wrong Industry Category (e.g.: mohon rubah kategori industry menjadi ‘toys &amp; games store)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mmkat5n3-0i1hnz-959\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5n3-f1m4ce-960\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouiu-ikxllx-387\">Open Admin Dashboard → channel activation tab → click OVO → search merchant by its merchant name → click edit</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5n3-54on07-961\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouiu-z8w078-388\">Revise Merchant Category based on OVO remarks → click save </p></li></ul></th></tr></tbody></table></div><ul data-block-id=\"mmkat5n3-wfqed7-962\"><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5n3-ykjojx-963\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouiu-1kuikp-389\">Change status to <em>new_submission</em></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmkat5n3-1cgrad-964\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouiu-tvfbzu-390\">and the merchant will be included in the next submission </p></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmszouiu-dka20w-391\"></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmkat5n3-rhoxbo-965\"><a id=\"_7ygm1uq0mjrb\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><p data-block-id=\"mmszouiu-ps2k03-392\"></p>","SeoTitle":"OVO","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"OVO","Slug":"ovo-1","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"OVO","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"OVO","Slug":"ovo-1","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"OVO","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"OVO","Slug":"ovo-1","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"OVO","Description":null}]